data.title: Wiz Khalifa Biography
data.meta_description: A behind-the-scene look at the life of Wiz Khalifa.
data.text:
"See You Again" featuring Charlie Puth is one of Wiz Khalifa's most popular songs, known for its emotional lyrics and connection to the movie "Furious 7."

Wiz Khalifa has mentioned that his favorite strain of marijuana is Khalifa Kush, which he helped develop.

Wiz Khalifa was inspired by his love for fashion and personal style, leading him to launch his own clothing line called "Taylor Gang."

Wiz Khalifa's stage name was inspired by the Arabic word "Khalifa," which means successor. He added "Wiz" as a short form of "wisdom," signifying his wise mindset.

Wiz Khalifa is known for his dedication to fitness, often incorporating boxing and martial arts into his workout routine to stay in shape and maintain his energy on stage.

Wiz Khalifa is a talented artist not only in music but also in visual arts. He is known for his skills in drawing and painting.

Wiz Khalifa holds a black belt in Taekwondo, showcasing his dedication to martial arts and physical fitness.

He is a passionate advocate for the legalization of marijuana and has his own line of cannabis products called Khalifa Kush.

Wiz Khalifa is a dedicated father to his son Sebastian, often sharing heartwarming moments of their relationship on social media.
